NOTE
This system, of course, provides help on OctaMED. So in these
pages, you'll find plenty on how to use MIDI with OctaMED, but very
little on what MIDI is all about (apart from some very basic
information).

There are several good books on MIDI about. Especially watch out
for the prolific author R. A. Penfold.
@ENDNODE


@NODE f7 "Using ARexx with OctaMED"
Select a topic for information and `how-to' guides.

