    @{" ARexx features " LINK F7.guide/f7_arfe}

NOTE
For more details on using ARexx with OctaMED, please read the
programmer's own documention, OctaMED_ARexx.doc.

General information on ARexx itself is outside the scope of the
OctaMED documentation. There are several good books on ARexx
around. You could also try to get hold of the shareware ARexxGuide
by Robin Evans.
@ENDNODE


